🎯 Project Overview
Cosmic Soul Reader is an immersive 3D astrological web application built with React that provides users with personalized cosmic readings, zodiac insights, and soul compatibility analysis. The app features stunning visual effects, animations, and an intuitive multi-step form interface.

Key Features
🌟 3D animated loader with tarot card effects
🎨 Glass morphism UI with cosmic themes
🔮 Multi-step soul reading form
✨ Particle effects and floating orbs
🎵 Sound effects and audio feedback
📱 Responsive design with mobile support
🌙 Multiple theme support (dark, light, nebula)
🛠 Technology Stack
Core Technologies
React 18.2.0 - UI framework
Vite 5.0.10 - Build tool and dev server
Tailwind CSS 3.4.0 - Utility-first CSS framework
Framer Motion 10.16.16 - Animation library
State Management
Zustand 4.4.7 - Lightweight state management
Zustand Persist - State persistence
3D & Animation
Three.js 0.160.0 - 3D graphics
@react-three/fiber 8.15.12 - React Three.js renderer
@react-three/drei 9.92.7 - Three.js helpers
GSAP 3.12.4 - Advanced animations
Audio & Effects
Howler.js 2.2.4 - Audio management
React Icons 5.0.1 - Icon library
Form Handling
React Hook Form 7.49.2 - Form management
Zod 3.22.4 - Schema validation
